-- China Expresses Support for Kim Jong Un, Yonhap Says
-- B y   S a n g w o n   Y o o n
-- 2011-12-19T13:24:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-19/china-expresses-support-for-kim-jong-un-yonhap-says.html
China  expressed support for North
Korea’s Kim Jong Un in a condolence message about the death of
his father  Kim Jong Il , Yonhap news reported today.  North Korea will become a strong and prosperous socialist
nation under the Workers’ Party of Korea and Kim Jong Un’s
leadership, according to the Korean language report, which cited
an official statement from the Chinese leadership.  China’s Xinhua News Agency earlier today reported that the
nation had offered its “deep condolences” on the death of Kim
Jong Il.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sangwon Yoon in Seoul at 
 syoon32@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
